&lt;/p>
&lt;ol start="4">
&lt;li>Screw each piece of wood to each other using two screws peer corner.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>
&lt;img src="https://iamjeremie.me/post/2022-11/create-a-no-dig-raised-bed-charles-dowding/images/step4-build-the-bed-frame.jpg"
