>
&lt;/p>
&lt;ol start="5">
&lt;li>Fill the bed with the least decomposed compost. It won&amp;rsquo;t fill the bed completely. You will want to firm it up with a shovel.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Apply the second layer with a more mature compost (10 month old for Charles&amp;rsquo;s compost). Firm it up again.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Finish with the most mature compost (16 month old in the vlog).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Plant your seedlings&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Water the seedlings depending on the season and your climate.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
